From e1eb1c37dd96242575388e8df38fb6b3b2b675d7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?=C3=98yvind=20Harboe?= <oyvind@ascenium.com>
Date: Sat, 16 May 2026 20:26:09 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] environment.bzl: pull src OrfsDepInfo.files into
 source_inputs

Without this, orfs_gds (and any other stage rule whose src is a
previous _make_impl stage) only sees its own ctx.files.data plus
OrfsInfo.{additional_gds,additional_lefs,additional_libs}.  Those
OrfsInfo.additional_* depsets are populated only from `deps`
(block macros), so the design's own ADDITIONAL_LEFS / ADDITIONAL_GDS
sources from config.mk's `$(wildcard $(DESIGN_DIR)/lef/*.lef)`
never propagate to stages past the one that consumed them as
ctx.files.data.

For orfs_gds specifically (which is invoked standalone by
orfs_blender with src=orfs_final and no data=), the 6_gds.args.mk
correctly inherits ADDITIONAL_LEFS via OrfsInfo.arguments, so the
make recipe writes the macro LEF paths into klayout.lyt -- but
klayout then opens those paths under the sandbox and fails with
errno=2, e.g.:

  RuntimeError: Unable to open file:
    .../sandbox/.../execroot/_main/flow/designs/sky130hd/microwatt/lef/Microwatt_FP_DFFRFile.lef

Propagating src's OrfsDepInfo.files (which carries the previous
stage's ctx.files.src + ctx.files.data + extra_configs but NOT its
logs/reports) makes the per-stage `data` files follow the
orfs_final -> orfs_gds chain automatically.  depset dedup keeps
the inputs tractable across the rest of the synth -> final chain.

Why OrfsDepInfo.files and not DefaultInfo.default_runfiles.files:
the latter also carries the previous stage's logs, which are
read-only in the sandbox and collide with the new stage's
same-named log writes (Permission denied on logs/.../6_1_merge.log).

Tested with sky130hd/microwatt (which has ADDITIONAL_LEFS for
Microwatt_FP_DFFRFile / RAM32_1RW1R / RAM512 / multiply_add_64x64
IP macros).
---
 private/environment.bzl | 14 ++++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 14 insertions(+)

diff --git a/private/environment.bzl b/private/environment.bzl
index f6df134..85dcbde 100644
--- a/private/environment.bzl
+++ b/private/environment.bzl
@@ -4,6 +4,7 @@ load("@bazel_skylib//rules:common_settings.bzl", "BuildSettingInfo")
 load(
     "//private:providers.bzl",
     "LoggingInfo",
+    "OrfsDepInfo",
     "OrfsInfo",
     "PdkInfo",
     "TopInfo",
@@ -175,6 +176,19 @@ def source_inputs(ctx):
     return depset(
         ctx.files.src,
         transitive = [
+            # Pull in src's OrfsDepInfo.files so action inputs include
+            # the design's per-stage source files (sources= -> data= via
+            # get_sources, e.g. ADDITIONAL_LEFS from $(wildcard
+            # $(DESIGN_DIR)/lef/*.lef)). OrfsInfo.additional_lefs only
+            # carries block-macro LEFs from deps, not the design's own
+            # macro LEFs, so without this propagation orfs_gds runs with
+            # the LEF paths in args.mk but the LEF files missing from the
+            # sandbox -- klayout def2stream fails errno=2 on first read.
+            # We pick OrfsDepInfo.files rather than default_runfiles.files
+            # because the latter also carries the previous stage's logs,
+            # which are read-only in the sandbox and collide with the new
+            # stage's same-named log writes (Permission denied).
+            ctx.attr.src[OrfsDepInfo].files,
             ctx.attr.src[OrfsInfo].additional_gds,
             ctx.attr.src[OrfsInfo].additional_lefs,
             ctx.attr.src[OrfsInfo].additional_libs,
